HEADWORD: Rutilant
<hw>Ru"ti*lant</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>rutilans</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>rutilare</ets> to have a reddish
